Labels.description: MinIO object storage is fundamentally different. Designed for performance and the S3 API, it is 100% open-source. This base image is freely redistributable, but Red Hat only supports Red Hat technologies through subscriptions for Red Hat products. This image is maintained by Red Hat and updated regularly.
